♪I will be known as the fearless one♪

12
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:39,780
=Douluo Continent=

13
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:42,780
=Episode 2=

14
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,760
Never let anyone see

15
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,720
the hammer in your left hand.

16
00:01:48,910 --> 00:01:50,800
Never mention Xuan Tian Records

17
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,510
to anyone.

18
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:56,190
You have to walk on your own.

19
00:02:00,190 --> 00:02:00,830
What happened?

20
00:02:02,550 --> 00:02:03,630
I forgot the nails.

21
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:06,720
There's nothing to do with the nails.

22
00:02:07,270 --> 00:02:08,440
The reason I taught you to do ironwork

23
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:11,120
is to let you learn Xuan Yu Hand.

24
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:12,910
I know.

25
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:15,830
I just can't bear to leave it
because I did that for a long time.

26
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,160
Just take it and go.

27
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,630
What else?

28
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,630
It's hard to give up the work
that has been done for a long time,

29
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:29,440
not to mention the people.

30
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:38,520
Dad, I'm a bit worried about you.

31
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,000
Why should you be worried?

32
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,520
Actually, my greatest worry is that

33
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,470
you'll be lonely

34
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,190
when I'm not here.

35
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:55,030
You won't tell me about

36
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:56,080
my mom,

37
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:57,390
but I know

38
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,030
you always miss her.

39
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,030
You drink every day

40
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,670
because you feel sad.

41
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,190
What nonsense are you talking about?

42
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,190
You can go. I won't drink anymore.

43
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,240
Dad,

44
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,830
what if I stay here?

45
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,520
Don't you want to be a Soul Master?

46
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:17,320
You can't endure the difficulties,

47
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,440
or do you think you are too foolish?

48
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:22,000
Since you've made up your mind,

49
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,800
don't give up easily.

50
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:27,880
Dad,

51
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,960
if I graduate from

52
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,440
the Soul Master School,

53
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,160
would you tell me

54
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,720
everything about the family?

55
00:03:33,670 --> 00:03:35,520
It depends on your ability,

56
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,110
whether you can afford it all by then.

57
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,160
Then I must be

58
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,160
the strongest Soul Master.

59
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,960
Be careful.

60
00:03:47,830 --> 00:03:49,750
You have to keep
Xuan Tian Records a secret,

61
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,670
but you can use your ability.

62
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:54,160
But my eyes will be purple.

63
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,880
What if someone else sees it?

64
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,520
The ability of a Soul Master is strange.

65
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:58,910
This is nothing.

66
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:00,160
Dad,

67
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:01,960
you know it well.

68
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,000
When you're practicing Martial Soul,

69
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:08,030
don't forget to perform
Xuan Tian Strike at the same time.

70
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,750
I got it.

71
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:12,190
You can go.

72
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,670
If you miss me,

73
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,350
tell Village Head
to ask me to return.

74
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,480
Okay.

75
00:04:42,670 --> 00:04:43,320
I have to go.

76
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,480
Village Head, we can go now.

77
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,510
Let's go.

78
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:40,760
Here we are.

79
00:05:55,350 --> 00:05:56,670
Don't stare at the headmaster.

80
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:57,600
It is impolite.

81
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,270
He's the headmaster?

82
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,760
Look at the passers-by.

83
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:05,920
Who dares to lie down at the entrance?

84
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:06,790
If he's not the headmaster,

85
00:06:06,790 --> 00:06:08,600
at least he's the person
in charge of the school.

86
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,200
Coming for school admission?

87
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,830
My name is Tang San,
from Saint of Soul Village.

88
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:17,160
He is our village head.

89
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,160
This year...

90
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,640
Stop.

91
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:20,440
Come over here.

92
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,040
Go.

93
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,950
Show me your Martial Soul.

94
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,480
You can go in.

95
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,640
Are you the headmaster or...

96
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,110
What are you doing here?

97
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,600
Who are you? Who said you can come here?

98
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:46,070
It says "Soul Master School"
at the entrance,

99
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,110
don't you see that?

100
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,640
This is not a place where

101
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,070
everyone can come in, understand?

102
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,200
Yes.

103
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,720
Please don't be mad.

104
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,480
Someone recommended us to come here,

105
00:06:54,550 --> 00:06:55,640
so we're here for school admission.

106
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,320
Can you tell us

107
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,720
what do we have to do

108
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,040
for registration?

109
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:00,550
Coming for school admission?

110
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:01,390
Yes.

111
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,670
I'll help the Office of Administration
to check on you.

112
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,790
Show me your recommendation letters.

113
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,600
Recommendation letter...

114
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,720
We don't have a recommendation letter.

115
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,270
You don't have it?

116
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,600
Get out!

117
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:11,830
-You!
-No!

118
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,160
By the way, Tang San

119
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,230
has a recommendation badge
from Martial Soul Hall.

120
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:15,880
You can take a look.

121
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,480
This is the recommendation badge
of Martial Soul Hall.

122
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,070
Take it.

123
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:22,670
Hurry.

124
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:23,790
It allows you

125
00:07:23,790 --> 00:07:25,640
to become an attached student
in the Beginner School in Nuoding City.

126
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:27,880
Your food, accommodation
and tuition fees are free.

127
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,880
Bring it with you
when you go to register.

128
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,720
He said that with
this recommendation badge,

129
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,390
Tang San can attend school for free.

130
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,040
The recommendation badge
of Martial Soul Hall?

131
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,760
-Yes.
-Yes.

132
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,350
Why would great people
from Martial Soul Hall

133
00:07:38,350 --> 00:07:39,760
recommend this brat

134
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:41,320
and let him become an attached student?

135
00:07:42,110 --> 00:07:42,480
I...

136
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,670
It's fake, isn't it?

137
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,600
What do you mean?

138
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,550
No, Tang San.

139
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:47,760
It's true. He is recommended
by Officer Su Yun Tao,

140
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:49,200
the officer of Martial Soul Hall.

141
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,480
Who are you?

142
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,200
I'm the village head of
Saint of Soul Village.

143
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,720
I'm sending Tang San here.

144
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,040
Do you have a recommendation badge too?

145
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,550
No, I don't have it.

146
00:07:58,830 --> 00:07:59,440
You don't have it?

147
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:00,640
Get out!

148
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,440
No.

149
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,830
No, Tang San.

150
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,000
I'll send you here.

151
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:09,440
You go in and settle down yourself,

152
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,600
okay?

153
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:14,070
What's with that look?

154
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,320
Are you feeling mad?

155
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,480
Are you feeling mad?

156
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,550
Don't stop him.

157
00:08:17,550 --> 00:08:18,270
Are you feeling mad?

158
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,640
Stay out of trouble.
Go to school first.

159
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,440
No wonder.

160
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,350
No great man

161
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:22,880
will ever come from that hellhole.

162
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,000
You're just an uncultured swine.

163
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:24,720
What?

164
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,350
That's enough, Liu Long.

165
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:27,950
Young Master Xiao.

166
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,480
-He...
-I heard everything.

167
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,480
How can a student of Nuoding School

168
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,600
bully others

169
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,040
and humiliate an older person?

170
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:34,600
I...

171
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,200
Please don't be mad.

172
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,600
I apologize on his behalf.

173
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,670
It's okay.

174
00:08:42,110 --> 00:08:43,030
You're a new student, right?

175
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,320
My family name is Xiao.

176
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,150
My name is Tang San.

177
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:49,280
Take your hand off.

178
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,520
Do you know who Young Master Xiao is?

179
00:08:52,710 --> 00:08:55,550
He is the son of
the governor of Nuoding City.

180
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:56,470
You're just an uncultured swine.

181
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:57,640
Do you think you can
shake hands with Young Master Xiao?

182
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,150
Liu Long!

183
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:01,760
Welcome.

184
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,080
He always speaks abruptly.
Don't mind him.

185
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,670
We're all students here.
Let's get along well.

186
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,230
Okay.

187
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,230
By the way,

188
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:12,590
I run the Student Martial Club.

189
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:14,350
It aims to help all new students.

190
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,470
It's at the small plaza over there.

191
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:17,960
If you're interested,

192
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,400
you can fill in an application
to join the club.

193
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,790
All of us will learn together in the future,

194
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,000
so we should help each other.

195
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:23,960
Go.

196
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,200
I'll go and take a look
when I'm free later.

197
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:27,200
Okay.

198
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,640
Welcome to Nuoding School.

199
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,400
Please come inside.

200
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,350
You should go in. I'll go back now.

201
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,960
Alright. Be careful, Village Head.

202
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:35,230
I'll go back and visit you
during school holidays.

203
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:37,110
Alright, you should be careful too.

204
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,000
I'll get going.

205
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,790
Be careful.

206
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:40,880
Alright!

207
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,110
I forgot to ask you just now.

208
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,760
Since you are recommended by
Martial Soul Hall,

209
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:50,960
then your Martial Soul

210
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,880
must be something special.

211
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:54,640
I just showed

212
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:56,960
my Martial Soul to the teacher.

213
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,520
He is just a handyman of our school.

214
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,760
Young Master Xiao asked you a question.

215
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:05,710
What is your Martial Soul?

216
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:08,840
Blue Silver Plant.

217
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:12,030
Isn't that a useless Martial Soul?

218
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,030
Why would Martial Soul Hall

219
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:15,150
recommend such a useless person?

220
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:16,350
Liu Long.

221
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:19,960
How strong is your Soul Power?

222
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:23,790
I have full Soul Power.

223
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,440
You're born with full Soul Power?

224
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,200
That's a rare thing,

225
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,350
but your Martial Soul is...

226
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:37,320
Anyway,

227
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,520
I'd like to sincerely invite you

228
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,440
to join my Martial Club.

229
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,280
Thank you.

230
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:51,200
Useless.

231
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,760
Who hit me?

232
00:10:58,520 --> 00:10:59,670
It's so weird.

233
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:18,960
Are you looking for me? What's up？

234
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,280
Show me your Martial Soul again.

235
00:11:21,230 --> 00:11:22,710
Didn't you just see it?

236
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,840
I didn't see it clearly.

237
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,280
I mean, I didn't see it clearly,

238
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,230
it's not that I didn't see it at all.

239
00:11:31,230 --> 00:11:32,150
I'm not blind.

240
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,960
I'm sorry. I misunderstood.

241
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:39,110
Are you really
born with full Soul Power?

242
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:41,470
It was confirmed by Officer Su Yun Tao,

243
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:43,110
the officer of Martial Soul Hall.

244
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:46,910
Then it should be right.

245
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,590
Show me the Martial Soul
in your left hand.

246
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:53,320
I don't know what you're talking about.

247
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,840
According to my research on 647 people

248
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,710
with Blue Silver Plant,

249
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:01,150
there are a total of
16 people with Soul Power,

250
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:03,030
and you're born with full Soul Power.

251
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:04,880
The size of an innate Soul Power
is proportional

252
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,520
to the quality of the Martial Soul.

253
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:08,280
If your Martial Soul
is Blue Silver Plant only,

254
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,400
you will never be able

255
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,400
to reach the state of full Soul Power.

256
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:11,760
So, I'm sure that

257
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,640
you should have another Martial Soul,

258
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,320
and this Martial Soul is very powerful.

259
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:19,110
There is an exception to every rule.

260
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,880
Perhaps I'm the exception.

261
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,110
There is an exception to every rule,

262
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:23,670
but there's no exception
for Blue Silver Plant.

263
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:25,030
According to my research on

264
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:25,960
Martial Soul for so many years,

265
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:26,550
I'm sure that

266
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:27,550
you should have another

267
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,590
very powerful Martial Soul

268
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:29,590
to provide you with Soul Power.

269
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:30,960
And you're the third person
who is one in a million

270
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,030
in the last hundred years
on the Douluo Continent

271
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,910
with Twin Martial Souls.

272
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,590
You look so surprised.

273
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,280
I don't quite understand
what you're saying,

274
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,440
but I think it's very powerful.

275
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,350
So,

276
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:47,910
let me see the Martial Soul
in your left hand.

277
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:49,760
I've told you that

278
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,470
I really don't have any
Twin Martial Souls.

279
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,080
Do you mean that

280
00:12:54,590 --> 00:12:55,760
my theory is wrong?

