00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:56,880
I didn't say that.

282
00:12:57,350 --> 00:12:58,840
My theory can't go wrong.

283
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,640
You're absolutely of Twin Martial Souls.

284
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,670
It's okay if you don't want to admit it.

285
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:03,470
It's up to you.

286
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,790
Why are you still wasting time here?

287
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,080
The Office of Administration is
short of helpers. Go carry the books.

288
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:08,350
I'll go now.

289
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,030
Are you a new student?

290
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:11,320
I'm an attached student.

291
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,230
All attached students
live in Dorm Seven.

292
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:15,000
Don't listen to his crap.
He's wasting your time.

293
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,520
You're not a teacher.

294
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,910
I'm not a teacher,

295
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,590
I'm just a guest

296
00:13:21,590 --> 00:13:23,000
who gets free meals here.

297
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,320
You can call me Master

298
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:25,230
as they do.

299
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:26,880
Okay.

300
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:29,350
Master, if there's nothing else,
I'll leave now.

301
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,000
Follow me.

302
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:33,520
I'll bring you to the registration.

303
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,280
Students usually attend
classes in the morning,

304
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:40,640
and they're free to do anything
in the afternoon and evening.

305
00:13:41,590 --> 00:13:42,840
Private fighting is
prohibited in the school,

306
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,320
but all students

307
00:13:44,590 --> 00:13:46,400
are allowed to compete
at the training ground.

308
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,670
Therefore, most of the students

309
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,400
will book a slot at
the training ground after class

310
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:51,550
to practice their skills
among others.

311
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,710
Of course,

312
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,790
you can come and learn from me.

313
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,520
Blue Silver Plant is
not a useless Martial Soul.

314
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:57,960
In this school,

315
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,320
I'm the only one who can guide you.

316
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,400
You're really a smart kid.

317
00:14:05,710 --> 00:14:07,150
There are three reasons
why you don't answer me.

318
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,200
Firstly,

319
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,080
you're not in a hurry to reject me

320
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,150
so that you won't offend me.

321
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:12,230
Secondly,

322
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:13,910
you're thinking about one question.

323
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,320
Since we've just met,

324
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,030
why should you become my student?

325
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:18,080
Thirdly,

326
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:19,670
you don't believe that I'm the only one

327
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:20,840
who can guide you in this school.

328
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,230
That's not what I'm thinking.

329
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,590
That is Xiao Chen Yu's
Student Martial Club.

330
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:32,280
What are they doing?

331
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,350
The first step to join
Student Martial Club is

332
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,470
to kill these rabbits.

333
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,030
Why?

334
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,080
If a Soul Master wants
to upgrade his Soul Ring,

335
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:44,080
he must hunt and kill Soul Beasts.

336
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:45,910
Xiao Chen Yu is trying

337
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,470
to make new students get used to

338
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:49,350
killing brutally from the beginning,

339
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,150
so they would
become a Soul Master later.

340
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:54,400
Are these Soul Beasts?

341
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:55,470
No.

342
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,030
They're just ordinary rabbits.

343
00:14:57,590 --> 00:14:58,910
They're using their lives

344
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,520
to toughen up their hearts.

345
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:20,400
(Nuoding School)
Nuoding's Soul Master Begin...

346
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,080
Nuoding...

347
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,280
Not bad.

348
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:27,910
Should I stop her for you?

349
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,640
Where is the "Beginner"?

350
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:40,080
Is this Nuoding's
Beginner Soul Master School?

351
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:41,760
Yes.

352
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:43,230
Then why is there

353
00:15:43,230 --> 00:15:45,030
