your Martial Soul in future,

421
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,190
will you choose to let it go?

422
00:18:02,950 --> 00:18:04,280
As long as it doesn't hurt humans,

423
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:05,560
I won't kill it.

424
00:18:07,230 --> 00:18:09,310
