those attached students.

548
00:24:00,230 --> 00:24:01,070
I took it for you.

549
00:24:01,590 --> 00:24:02,350
Thank you, Master.

550
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:03,830
Private fighting is
prohibited in the school.

551
00:24:04,190 --> 00:24:06,000
Don't get yourself involved in a fight.

552
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:07,830
I...

553
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,520
