using your Martial Soul?

554
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:18,830
Didn't you use your
Martial Soul just now?

555
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:20,190
I didn't use it.

556
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,110
Then how did you catch him?

557
00:24:23,590 --> 00:24:24,520
I caught him just like that.

558
00:24:25,190 --> 00:24:25,830
Let's fight.

559
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,000
No, I don't fight.

560
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:29,590
The winner will be the boss.

561
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:31,640
I don't want to be the boss.

